  "title": "ATTC Trainer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Conduct training for CoreTrade and SEC(K) courses.</li>\n  <li>Maintain safe and clean training environment (Classrooms, training/test bays, workshop, office and store).</li>\n  <li>Maintain functionality and control stock for training equipment, devices, utilities, materials and etc.</li>\n  <li>Maintain high CoreTrade test passing rate of 90%.</li>\n  <li>Maintain proper training/test documentation for auditing.</li>\n  <li>Carry out adhoc work and complete tasks given by the Training Manager</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>At least 4 years of working experience in Constuction industry </li>\n  <li>Possess a SEC(K) cert by BCA </li>\n</ol>",
